Class StagedQuest

  • java.lang.Object

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class StagedQuest
extends AbstractQuest<StagedQuest>
    A Quest which seperates it's Objectives out into Stages, so that they must be completed one-by-one, in an ordered fashion.
